Vorkath is an undead blue dragon boss found in the crater on the island of Ungael north of the Fremennik Province.

Attack Styles - Melee, Ranged, Magic, Special, Dragonfire
Immunities - Poison, Venom
Slayer categories - Blue Dragon, Zombie
